<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA5">
<l>aṭivaṇṇan tāmarai yaṉṟulakan tāyōṉ</l>
<l>paṭivaṇṇam pārkkaṭaṉīr vaṇṇa – muṭivaṇṇa</l>
<l>mōrāḻi veyyō ṉoḷiyumaḵ taṉṟē</l>
<l>yārāḻi koṇṭāṟ kaḻaku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The feet of him who that day spread over the world are the colour of lotuses,</l>
<l>the colour of [his] body is the colour of the vast ocean’s water, the colour of [his]</l> 
<l>crown is the light of the hot one with a single wheel . That, isn’t it,</l>
<l>is the beauty of him who has the precious discus.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
